EmailTemplate.name: Parental Leave
EmailTemplate.subject: Parental Leave
EmailTemplate.textOnly:
Thank you for reaching out to the HR Ops Team about your upcoming leave of absence. Your manager should receive notification from CIGNA that an FMLA leave request is pending and/or has been approved. Since this leave is related to the birth or placement of a child for adoption or foster care, it could also qualify under our Parental leave policy. Please reference the attached policy for eligibility, benefit details, and notification requirements.
Thank you,
HR Operations Team
